---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contribute to ICN" description="How to contribute to the InterCooperative Network project.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary border border-accent-primary/30 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block">
          CONTRIBUTE
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Contribute to ICN</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          ICN is open source and built by a community of contributors.
          Here's how you can help.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <!-- Code Contributions -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-6">Code Contributions</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            ICN is written in Rust. The codebase is well-tested with 1,134+ tests
            and organized into 16 specialized crates.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm text-light-slate mb-6">
            <pre># Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn
cd icn

# Run tests
cargo test

# Build
cargo build --release</pre>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-primary transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Source Code</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Browse the repository on GitHub</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-primary transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Good First Issues</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Issues suitable for newcomers</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Documentation -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-blue/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-blue mb-6">Documentation</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Good documentation is essential. Help improve the docs by fixing typos,
            clarifying explanations, or adding examples.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/tree/main/docs"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-blue transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">ICN Docs</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Technical documentation in the main repo</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn-website"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-blue transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Website</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">This website's source code</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testing -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-purple/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-purple mb-6">Testing & Bug Reports</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Help us find and fix bugs. Run ICN locally, test features, and report
            issues you encounter.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-purple">•</span>
              <span>Clone and build the project locally</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-purple">•</span>
              <span>Test the Pilot Web UI and daemon functionality</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-purple">•</span>
              <span>Report bugs with clear reproduction steps</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-purple">•</span>
              <span>Suggest improvements and new features</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/issues"
             target="_blank"
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-purple text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-purple/90 transition-colors">
            Report an Issue
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Community -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow mb-6">Community Participation</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Not a developer? You can still contribute by participating in discussions,
            helping answer questions, and spreading the word about ICN.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/GCWKPWdvgH"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-glow transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Discord</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Chat with the community</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/discussions"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-glow transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Discussions</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Participate in longer-form conversations</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contribution Guidelines -->
        <div class="bg-accent-glow/10 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/30">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow mb-4">Contribution Guidelines</h2>
          <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-glow font-bold">1.</span>
              <span>Fork the repository and create a feature branch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-glow font-bold">2.</span>
              <span>Write tests for new functionality</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-glow font-bold">3.</span>
              <span>Ensure all tests pass with <code class="bg-midnight-navy px-2 py-1 rounded">cargo test</code></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-glow font-bold">4.</span>
              <span>Format code with <code class="bg-midnight-navy px-2 py-1 rounded">cargo fmt</code></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-glow font-bold">5.</span>
              <span>Submit a pull request with a clear description</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
